(185, '<p>Uso indevido de celular vira rotina nas escolas<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Na &nbsp;Am&eacute;rica &nbsp;Latina, &nbsp;estima?se &nbsp;que &nbsp;60% &nbsp;das &nbsp;crian&ccedil;as &nbsp;ganham &nbsp;o &nbsp;seu &nbsp;primeiro &nbsp;telefone &nbsp;celular &nbsp;aos &nbsp;12 &nbsp;anos<br />\r\nEspecificamente no Brasil, uma em cada tr&ecirc;s crian&ccedil;as acessa a internet por dispositivos m&oacute;veis e a m&eacute;dia de idade para&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;se &nbsp;ganhar &nbsp;um &nbsp;celular &nbsp;tem &nbsp;sido &nbsp;8 &nbsp;anos. &nbsp;Esses &nbsp;n&uacute;meros &nbsp;evidenciam &nbsp;o &nbsp;alcance &nbsp;tecnol&oacute;gico &nbsp;na &nbsp;nova &nbsp;gera&ccedil;&atilde;o &nbsp;de&nbsp;<br />\r\nbrasileirinhos conectados, que segundo uma &nbsp;recente pesquisa do &nbsp;Instituto &nbsp;iStart, &ndash; &oacute;rg&atilde;o que &nbsp;tem a miss&atilde;o de &nbsp;levar&nbsp;<br />\r\nmais &nbsp;educa&ccedil;&atilde;o &nbsp;em &nbsp;&Eacute;tica &nbsp;e &nbsp;Seguran&ccedil;a &nbsp;Digital &nbsp;para &nbsp;as &nbsp;fam&iacute;lias &nbsp;brasileiras &nbsp;&ndash; &nbsp;ainda &nbsp;n&atilde;o &nbsp;est&aacute; &nbsp;recebendo &nbsp;orienta&ccedil;&otilde;es&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;adequadas por parte da fam&iacute;lia e at&eacute; da escola para o uso &eacute;tico, legal, seguro e saud&aacute;vel destes dispositivos digitais<br />\r\nO &nbsp;estudo &nbsp;aponta &nbsp;que &nbsp;o &nbsp;mau &nbsp;uso &nbsp;das &nbsp;novas &nbsp;ferramentas &nbsp;tecnol&oacute;gicas &nbsp;no &nbsp;ambiente &nbsp;escolar &nbsp;&eacute; &nbsp;frequente &nbsp;e &nbsp;as&nbsp;<br />\r\ninstitui&ccedil;&otilde;es &nbsp;pesquisadas &nbsp;foram &nbsp;un&acirc;nimes &nbsp;ao &nbsp;afirmar &nbsp;que &nbsp;j&aacute; &nbsp;registraram &nbsp;em &nbsp;m&eacute;dia &nbsp;20 &nbsp;ocorr&ecirc;ncias &nbsp;de &nbsp;utiliza&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;inadequada dos dispositivos entre os alunos desde o in&iacute;cio do ano letivo de 2015. Os incidentes mais comuns t&ecirc;m sido:&nbsp;<br />\r\ncyberbullying &nbsp;(75%), &nbsp;distra&ccedil;&atilde;o, &nbsp;dispers&atilde;o &nbsp;e &nbsp;interfer&ecirc;ncia &nbsp;no &nbsp;andamento &nbsp;da &nbsp;aula &nbsp;por &nbsp;conta &nbsp;do &nbsp;manuseio &nbsp;do &nbsp;celular&nbsp;<br />\r\n(56,25%) e a exposi&ccedil;&atilde;o demasiada de &nbsp;intimidade com o compartilhamento de &nbsp;imagens &nbsp;&iacute;ntimas de menores de &nbsp;idade&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;(31,25%)<br />\r\nNa avalia&ccedil;&atilde;o da Dra. Patricia Peck Pinheiro, advogada especialista em Direito Digital e fundadora do Instituto iStart,&nbsp;<br />\r\nhoje o celular &eacute; uma ferramenta poderosa que funciona como a porta da rua digital, abrindo caminhos para as crian&ccedil;as&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;ficarem expostas a bilh&otilde;es de pessoas conectadas, onde n&atilde;o h&aacute; muros nem portas. &ldquo;Os pais devem alertar seus filhos&nbsp;<br />\r\nsobre estes riscos. Pelo Estatuto da Crian&ccedil;a e do Adolescente (ECA) , a crian&ccedil;a, que &eacute; o menor at&eacute; 12 anos incompletos,&nbsp;<br />\r\nn&atilde;o pode ficar desacompanhada de um adulto, seja em casa, na rua tradicional ou na internet. Sempre tem que haver&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;um adulto respons&aacute;vel supervisionando e assistindo.&rdquo;&nbsp;<br />\r\nA advogada enaltece que a atual &nbsp;realidade &nbsp;interconectada exige preparo para usar essas &nbsp;ferramentas de &nbsp;forma&nbsp;<br />\r\nsaud&aacute;vel e segura, pois qualquer descuido pode gerar muita dor de cabe&ccedil;a e danos bem reais. &ldquo;Pais e professores que&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;tiveram &nbsp;toda &nbsp;uma &nbsp;educa&ccedil;&atilde;o &nbsp;mais &nbsp;anal&oacute;gica &nbsp;hoje &nbsp;t&ecirc;m &nbsp;o &nbsp;desafio &nbsp;de &nbsp;precisarem &nbsp;orientar &nbsp;os &nbsp;jovens &nbsp;digitais &nbsp;sobre &nbsp;a&nbsp;<br />\r\nimport&acirc;ncia da boa conduta no uso destes recursos, ajudando?os a despertar essa vis&atilde;o cr&iacute;tica de que a moda passa,&nbsp;<br />\r\nmas o conte&uacute;do fica nas redes e se perpetua na web&rdquo;, afirma Patricia<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\nA Dra. Patricia Peck Pinheiro &eacute; advogada especialista em Direito Digital, formada pela Universidade de S&atilde;o Paulo,&nbsp;<br />\r\ncom especializa&ccedil;&atilde;o em neg&oacute;cios pela Harvard Business School, curso de Gest&atilde;o de Riscos pela Funda&ccedil;&atilde;o Dom Cabral e&nbsp;<br />\r\nMBA em marketing pela Madia Marketing School. &Eacute; S&oacute;cia Fundadora do escrit&oacute;rio Patricia Peck Pinheiro Advogados, da&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;empresa de cursos Patricia Peck Pinheiro Treinamentos e do &nbsp;Instituto &nbsp;iStart de &Eacute;tica Digital que conduz o Movimento&nbsp;<br />\r\nFam&iacute;lia mais Segura na Internet.<br />\r\n(Dispon&iacute;vel em: http://www.desafiosdaeducacao.com.br/blog/. Adaptado.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Analise&nbsp;as&nbsp;afirmativas&nbsp;a&nbsp;seguir.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI.Entre&nbsp;os&nbsp;incidentes&nbsp;mais&nbsp;comuns&nbsp;relatados&nbsp;no&nbsp;texto&nbsp;est&aacute;&nbsp;a&nbsp;distra&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;em&nbsp; sala&nbsp;de&nbsp;aula,&nbsp;muitas&nbsp;vezes&nbsp;com&nbsp;interfer&ecirc;ncias&nbsp; no&nbsp;andamento&nbsp;das&nbsp;aulas.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nII. Menores&nbsp; de&nbsp; idade&nbsp; com&nbsp; pouca&nbsp; orienta&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp; no&nbsp; manuseio&nbsp; dos&nbsp; equipamentos&nbsp; acabam&nbsp; tendo&nbsp; suas&nbsp; imagens&nbsp; &iacute;ntimas&nbsp; compartilhadas&nbsp;na&nbsp;web.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIII. &Eacute;&nbsp; comum&nbsp; encontrar&nbsp; crian&ccedil;as&nbsp; que&nbsp; est&atilde;o&nbsp; passando&nbsp; pelo&nbsp; cyberbullying,&nbsp; os&nbsp; celulares&nbsp; facilitam&nbsp; a&nbsp; agress&atilde;o&nbsp; que&nbsp; inclui&nbsp; amea&ccedil;as&nbsp;de&nbsp;dano&nbsp;ou&nbsp;intimida&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;excessiva.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEst&aacute;[&atilde;o]&nbsp;correta[a]&nbsp;a[s]&nbsp;afirmativa[s]</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start="1" style="list-style-type:upper-alpha">\r\n	<li>I,&nbsp;II&nbsp;e&nbsp;III.</li>\r\n	<li>III,&nbsp;apenas.</li>\r\n	<li>I&nbsp;e&nbsp;II,&nbsp;apenas.</li>\r\n	<li>II&nbsp;e&nbsp;III,&nbsp;apenas.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>Letra A.</p>\r\n', 4, 1, 1, '2017-02-04 20:57:07', 1),
(186, '<p>One of many JavaScript HTML methods is getElementById(). A correct example and description of its use is shown in:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start="1" style="list-style-type:upper-alpha">\r\n	<li>document.getElementById(&#39;image&#39;).href=&#39;imagem.gif&#39;; changes an HTML image by changing the href attribute of an&nbsp;&nbsp;tag.</li>\r\n	<li>document.getElementById(&quot;letter&quot;).innerHTML=&quot;Content&quot;; finds an HTML element with id=&quot;letter&quot; and changes the element content to &quot;Content&quot;.</li>\r\n	<li>document.getElementById(&quot;text&quot;).fontSize=&quot;25px&quot;; changes the font size of an HTML element with id=&quot;text&quot; to 25 pixels.</li>\r\n	<li>document.getElementById(&quot;text&quot;).display=&quot;none&quot;; hides the element with id=&quot;text&quot;.</li>\r\n	<li>document.getElementById(&quot;text&quot;).display=&quot;block&quot;; shows the element with id=&quot;text&quot;.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>Letra B.</p>\r\n', 4, 2, 1, '2017-02-18 13:08:00', 1),
(187, '<p>Considere a p&aacute;gina a seguir, constru&iacute;da com HTML5.</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n&lt;html&gt; \r\n    &lt;head&gt; \r\n        &lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt; \r\n        &lt;title&gt;Exemplo&lt;/title&gt; \r\n        &lt;style&gt; \r\n        \r\n<img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/mapastatic/57fbb068533f6005f1f5a6b9/imgs_assist_tecnolog_programador/i.png" />\r\n \r\n        &lt;/style&gt; \r\n    &lt;/head&gt; \r\n    &lt;body&gt; \r\n        &lt;h1&gt;Esportes&lt;/h1&gt; \r\n        &lt;p&gt;Texto sobre esportes&lt;/p&gt; \r\n        &lt;h2&gt;Olimp&iacute;adas&lt;/h2&gt; \r\n        &lt;p&gt;Par&aacute;grafo sobre as Olimp&iacute;adas&lt;/p&gt; \r\n        &lt;p&gt;Par&aacute;grafo sobre as Olimp&iacute;adas&lt;/p&gt; \r\n    &lt;/body&gt; \r\n&lt;/html&gt; \r\n </pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Para que todos os par&aacute;grafos ap&oacute;s a tag &lt;h2&gt; apare&ccedil;am com letra na cor azul, deve-se utilizar na lacuna I a instru&ccedil;&atilde;o CSS3</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start="1" style="list-style-type:upper-alpha">\r\n	<li>h2 + p {color:#0000FF}</li>\r\n	<li>h2 * p {color:#00FF00;}</li>\r\n	<li>h2 &gt; p {color:#0000FF}</li>\r\n	<li>h2 ^ p {color:#FF0000}</li>\r\n	<li>h2 ~ p {color:#0000FF}</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>Letra E.</p>\r\n', 4, 2, 2, '2017-02-26 22:35:36', 1),
(188, '<p>Em uma p&aacute;gina HTML h&aacute; um par&aacute;grafo vazio criado pela tag &lt;p id=&quot;local&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;. Em um bloco JavaScript da mesma p&aacute;gina, para inserir neste par&aacute;grafo a palavra Teresina, utiliza-se o comando</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start="1" style="list-style-type:upper-alpha">\r\n	<li>document.getElementById(&quot;local&quot;).innerHTML = &quot;Teresina&quot;;</li>\r\n	<li>document.getElement(&quot;p#demo&quot;).innerHTML = &quot;Teresina&quot;;</li>\r\n	<li>document.p[&quot;#local&quot;].value = &quot;Teresina&quot;;</li>\r\n	<li>document.demo.value = &quot;Teresina&quot;;</li>\r\n	<li>document.getElementByName(&quot;local&quot;).innerHTML = &quot;Teresina&quot;;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>Letra A.</p>\r\n', 4, 2, 1, '2017-02-18 13:09:37', 1),
(189, '<p>Considere uma p&aacute;gina HTML5 que possui um elemento</p>\r\n\r\n<p>contendo em seu interior um texto grande, de, aproximadamente, uma p&aacute;gina. Para colocar este texto em 3 colunas nos navegadores Chrome, Safari e Opera, utilizando CSS3, deve-se inserir, no bloco CSS incorporado, a instru&ccedil;&atilde;o</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start="1" style="list-style-type:upper-alpha">\r\n	<li>.texto{-webkit-column-count:3}</li>\r\n	<li>.texto{-moz-column-count:3}</li>\r\n	<li>#texto{column-count:3}</li>\r\n	<li>.texto{column-width:3}</li>\r\n	<li>.texto{-column-count-width:3}</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>Letra A.</p>\r\n', 4, 2, 1, '2017-02-18 13:10:22', 1),
(190, '<p>Considere a p&aacute;gina HTML abaixo, contida na mesma pasta da biblioteca jquery-2.1.4.min:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n \r\n&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt; \r\n&lt;html&gt; \r\n  &lt;head&gt; \r\n    &lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;jquery-2.1.4.min&quot;&gt; \r\n    &lt;/script&gt; \r\n    &lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt; \r\n      $(document).ready(function() { \r\n        $(&#39;button&#39;).click(function() { \r\n          $(&#39;<img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/mapastatic/566e98d86c696e09c900000e/imgs_prova_c03_tipo_001/I.PNG" />&#39;).css(&#39;background&#39;, &#39;red&#39;); \r\n        }); \r\n      }); \r\n    &lt;/script&gt; \r\n  &lt;/head&gt; \r\n    &lt;body&gt; \r\n        &lt;button type=&quot;button&quot;&gt;Aplicar&lt;/button&gt; \r\n        &lt;table border=&quot;1&quot;&gt; \r\n            &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;A&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; \r\n            &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;B&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; \r\n            &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;C&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; \r\n            &lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;D&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt; \r\n        &lt;/table&gt; \r\n    &lt;/body&gt; \r\n&lt;/html&gt; \r\n </pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Ao clicar no bot&atilde;o Aplicar, para que as letras B e D, contidas na tabela, fiquem com fundo na cor vermelha, deve-se preencher a lacuna I com</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start="1" style="list-style-type:upper-alpha">\r\n	<li>tr:even</li>\r\n	<li>td:eq(1,3)</li>\r\n	<li>tr:odd</li>\r\n	<li>td:cel(2,4)</li>\r\n	<li>tr:unpaired</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>Letra C.</p>\r\n', 4, 2, 1, '2017-02-18 13:12:52', 1),
(191, '<p>Um Programador deseja inserir no corpo de uma p&aacute;gina HTML uma anima&ccedil;&atilde;o .swf constru&iacute;da com Flash, um arquivo .html e uma imagem .jpeg. Para isso dever&aacute; utilizar os elementos</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start="1" style="list-style-type:upper-alpha">\r\n	<li>&lt;plugin&gt; ou &lt;object&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;embed&gt; ou &lt;object&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;object&gt; ou &lt;canvas&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;media&gt; ou &lt;embedded&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;img&gt; ou &lt;embed&gt;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>Letra B.</p>\r\n', 4, 2, 1, '2017-02-18 13:13:28', 1),
(192, '<p>&lt;html&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;head&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;title&gt;Prova&lt;/title&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;function ver() {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;var pontos = 0;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;if () {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;pontos++;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;document.getElementById(&quot;res&quot;).innerHTML = pontos;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/script&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;/head&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;body&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;form name=&quot;frm&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;p&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Quest&atilde;o 1 - CSS &eacute; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;q1&quot; value=&quot;a&quot;&gt; uma linguagem de programa&ccedil;&atilde;o.&lt;br&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;q1&quot; value=&quot;b&quot;&gt; um framework.&lt;br&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;q1&quot; value=&quot;c&quot;&gt; uma pr&aacute;tica de gest&atilde;o.&lt;br&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;q1&quot; value=&quot;d&quot;&gt; uma linguagem de estilos.&lt;br&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;q1&quot; value=&quot;e&quot;&gt; um modelo matem&aacute;tico.&lt;br&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;button&quot; onclick=&quot;ver();&quot; value=&quot;Ver Resultado&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/form&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;p id=&quot;res&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;/body&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Para que o comando if verifique se a op&ccedil;&atilde;o marcada como resposta na quest&atilde;o do formul&aacute;rio &eacute; a op&ccedil;&atilde;o d, que exibe o texto uma linguagem de estilos, a lacuna I deve ser preenchida por</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start="1" style="list-style-type:upper-alpha">\r\n	<li>document.frm.q1[3].checked=true</li>\r\n	<li>document.frm.q1[4].checked==true</li>\r\n	<li>document.frm.q1[3].checked</li>\r\n	<li>document.frm.q1.value[&#39;d&#39;].checked==true</li>\r\n	<li>document.frm.q1[4].checked</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>Letra D.</p>\r\n', 4, 1, 1, '2017-02-05 16:44:06', 0),
(193, '<p>Para que o navegador saiba explicitamente que a p&aacute;gina foi escrita na linguagem HTML5 &eacute; necess&aacute;rio inserir a instru&ccedil;&atilde;o</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start="1" style="list-style-type:upper-alpha">\r\n	<li>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 5.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/html5/ strict.dtd&quot;&gt; ap&oacute;s da tag &lt;html&gt;.</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt; antes da tag &lt;html&gt;.</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 5.0 Transitional//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/ TR/html5/loose.dtd&quot;&gt; antes da tag &lt;html&gt;.</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;!DOCTYPE html5 PUBLIC&gt; antes da tag &lt;html&gt;.</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 5.0 //PT-BR&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/html5/ html5.dtd&quot;&gt; antes da tag &lt;html&gt;.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>Letra B.</p>\r\n', 4, 2, 1, '2017-02-18 13:13:42', 1),
(194, '<p>&lt;html&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;head&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;title&gt;Prova&lt;/title&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;function ver() {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;var pontos = 0;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;if () {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;pontos++;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;document.getElementById(&quot;res&quot;).innerHTML = pontos;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;}<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/script&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;/head&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;body&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;form name=&quot;frm&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;p&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Quest&atilde;o 1 - CSS &eacute; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;q1&quot; value=&quot;a&quot;&gt; uma linguagem de programa&ccedil;&atilde;o.&lt;br&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;q1&quot; value=&quot;b&quot;&gt; um framework.&lt;br&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;q1&quot; value=&quot;c&quot;&gt; uma pr&aacute;tica de gest&atilde;o.&lt;br&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;q1&quot; value=&quot;d&quot;&gt; uma linguagem de estilos.&lt;br&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;radio&quot; name=&quot;q1&quot; value=&quot;e&quot;&gt; um modelo matem&aacute;tico.&lt;br&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;input type=&quot;button&quot; onclick=&quot;ver();&quot; value=&quot;Ver Resultado&quot;&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/form&gt;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;p id=&quot;res&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;/body&gt;<br />\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Para que o comando if verifique se a op&ccedil;&atilde;o marcada como resposta na quest&atilde;o do formul&aacute;rio &eacute; a op&ccedil;&atilde;o d, que exibe o texto uma linguagem de estilos, a lacuna I deve ser preenchida por</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start="1" style="list-style-type:upper-alpha">\r\n	<li>document.frm.q1[3].checked=true</li>\r\n	<li>document.frm.q1[4].checked==true</li>\r\n	<li>document.frm.q1[3].checked</li>\r\n	<li>document.frm.q1.value[&#39;d&#39;].checked==true</li>\r\n	<li>document.frm.q1[4].checked</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>Letra C.</p>\r\n', 4, 2, 1, '2017-02-18 13:16:33', 1),
(195, '<p>Para incluir uma foto chamada minhaimagem.png, que se encontra no diret&oacute;rio atual de uma p&aacute;gina HTML chamado diret&oacute;riodeimagens, ajustando o dimensionamento dessa foto para um quadrado com 280 pixels de lados, deve ser usada a tag HTML</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start="1" style="list-style-type:upper-alpha">\r\n	<li>&lt;img width=&quot;280px&quot; height=&quot;280px&quot; src=&quot;diretoriodeimagens/minhaimagem.png&quot;/&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;img align right=&quot;280px&quot; align left=&quot;280px&quot; src=&quot;diretoriodeimagens/ minhaimagem.png&quot;/&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;photo width=&quot;280px&quot; height=&quot;280px&quot; src=&quot;diretoriodeimagens/ minhaimagem.png&quot;/&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;photo vertical=&quot;280px&quot; horizontal=&quot;280px&quot; dir=&quot;diretoriodeimagens/ minhaimagem.png&quot;/&gt;</li>\r\n	<li>&lt;img width=&quot;280px&quot; height=&quot;280px&quot; path way=&quot;diretoriodeimagens/ minhaimagem.png&quot;/&gt;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>Letra A.</p>\r\n', 4, 2, 1, '2017-02-18 13:17:47', 1),
(196, '<p>Considere a p&aacute;gina HTML5 a seguir:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n\r\n &lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n &lt;html&gt; \r\n   &lt;head&gt;&lt;title&gt;&lt;/title&gt;&lt;/head&gt; \r\n   &lt;body&gt; \r\n     &lt;p id=&quot;dados&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt; \r\n     &lt;script&gt; \r\n        var campos = [&quot;ID&quot;, &quot;Nome&quot;, &quot;Endere&ccedil;o&quot;, &quot;Telefone&quot;]; \r\n        ??I  \r\n     &lt;/script&gt; \r\n   &lt;/body&gt; \r\n &lt;/html&gt; \r\n </pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Para exibir o conte&uacute;do da array campos no par&aacute;grafo identificado como dados deve-se utilizar na lacuna I a instru&ccedil;&atilde;o</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start="1" style="list-style-type:upper-alpha">\r\n	<li>document.getElementById(&quot;dados&quot;).innerHTML = campos.toString();</li>\r\n	<li>document.getElementById(&quot;dados&quot;).insertHTML = toString(campos);</li>\r\n	<li>document.target(&quot;campos&quot;) =campos.valueOf();</li>\r\n	<li>document.getParagraph(&quot;dados&quot;).innerHTML = campos.valueOf();</li>\r\n	<li>document.getElementById(&quot;dados&quot;).innerHTML = valueOf(campos);</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '<p>Letra A.</p>\r\n', 4, 2, 1, '2017-02-18 13:18:55', 1),
